  id: 4
  title: Lost and Found
  description: 'You take a step outside for some fresh air where you find a wallet
    on the ground. There''s no ID, but there''s a lot of other valuables in it.


    No
    one else is around. The owner probably wouldn''t notice if a litte bit went missing
    before you turn it into the lost and found.'
  options:
  - title: Take something
    description: <color=green>+$10</color>, become <color=red>Anxious</color> <color=#828282>(x5)</color>
    requirement: 
    conclusion: 'It might not be right, but a little money is nice. '
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 0}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: Anxious
  - title: Take something
    description: Earn <color=#D2D2D2>Credit Card</color>, become <color=red>Anxious</color>
      <color=#828282>(x5)</color>
    requirement: Requires an available item slot
    conclusion: 'It''ll probably get canceled anyway.


      How much could it really
      hurt?'
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 9bd200e811238f14c81b5051c321a7a3, type: 2}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: 
  - title: Take something
    description: Earn <color=#D2D2D2>Gift Card</color>, become <color=red>Anxious</color>
      <color=#828282>(x5)</color>
    requirement: Requires an available item slot
    conclusion: 'Most people forget to use these.


      You''re just making sure
      it doesn''t go to waste, right?'
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f54557b8b6e7b1240977791479001533, type: 2}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: 
  - title: Do the right thing
    description: <color=blue>+1</color> confidence
    requirement: 
    conclusion: 'You turn the wallet into the lost and found at the bar.


      It''s
      what you''d hope people would do if it was yours. '
    isHidden: 0
